<h2 id="my-co-founder">My Co-Founder</h2>
<p>It had been one year of dating my mainland chinese girlfriend. We met back in 2014 by chance at a fundraising event and 3 years later, somehow, started dating while still being separated by thousands of miles but thatâ€™s a story for another day.</p>

<p>I never fully understood what she did for a living but I knew she studied fashion design and that she owned a wedding dress rental company in China. I thought that was so cool. I was dating a real boss lady. Sometimes Iâ€™d be confused as to what she saw in me but then sheâ€™d ask me to make her a website or lend one of my other technical skills - my true value as a partnerâ€¦ free labor ;)</p>

